- **Statistical Weighting:** Statistical weighting in dual-modality configurations significantly enhances model performance by leveraging data diversity and modality-specific importance.
- **Human-Centered Modality Segmentation:** Human-centered design in segmenting modalities can amplify model effectiveness.
